E2F1AUD.original: ~z~And, it ain't exactly like Tony's operation is always completely above board.

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~那你是在掌控世界呢，还是在给哪个傻逼跑腿？

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~And we started getting into that Vespucci University toto? Remember that?

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~I think I know the cat that owns that shit.

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Yo. They's three of us. I ain't gonna have Henrique on my knee just so we can ride in this thing.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~哟，咱有三个人。我不会接受让Henrique坐我腿上的解决方案的。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Unfortunately, I ain't no poster child. I'm still hanging out with degenerates like you, ain't I?

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~and complaining about how life could be.

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~但是一家人不是说我们都住这儿，卖毒品给Alderney的乡巴佬，

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~－干到她眼镜都掉下来。~n~－呵呵呵呵呵，确有其事。

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~喂，我们走吧。老妈，我得走了，好吗？来，你收好。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Backs against the wall, bro. It's us or them.

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~with a good enough purity so we gonna be able to roll with your rich friends.

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~I'm sorry man, I just miss you and maybe I express myself coarsely, but we was like family.

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~我也不是学不了你。一个人跑路，

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~喂喂喂喂喂，我知道你看不起我们，知道你不把我们当回事。但就是这样我才会找你，兄弟。

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~是一批能让我们发家致富走向成功的好货。

E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~匿名号码，兄弟。信息不多，只有时间地点。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, bro. That was the moment when you put down the gun and picked up the pork sword.

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, dick sucking's well below board. You right.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~确实，舔屌这事见不得光，没错。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~~x~ Henrique, can you get the moron to shut up please?
~z~Yo, fuck that, you fucking amateurs. I'm outta here, man.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~哟，真操蛋，一群菜逼。我得溜了，哥们。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~We can't meet no connect with a police escort. We got to lose these fucks.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~有警察护送还怎么做生意，得甩掉这帮混蛋。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Just what we need for a friendly tête-à-tête.
~z~You ain't going back inside, L. We look after you.
~z~Product then profit then pussy: 'P.P.P.' That how it works, bro.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~派货，票子，泡妞，简称PPP。就是这么来的，兄弟。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, the last time we had something real coming down, I did two years.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~是吗，上次我们有大买卖的时候，我进去了两年。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Luis, take your life more seriously, baby. Please. Don't be like your father.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~Luis，你一定要好好活，宝贝。求你了。别像你爸那样。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~None that did anything. Them punks Oscar, Willy and Alonso did and look where they at.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~没一个成器的。Oscar、Willy和Alonso那几个混蛋成了事，看看他们现在在哪。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Chill, bro. We meeting a new business associate.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~淡定，兄弟。我们要去见新的合作伙伴。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Whoa whoa whoa whoa. This is Luis Lopez. He's our boy.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~喔喔喔喔，这是Luis Lopez，我们的人。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~You met Tony in that prison outreach program, too. From there on it was all up for you.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~你还通过囚犯再就业计划遇到了Tony。之后就是好日子了。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~You ain't on no date with your homo lover. Get a car me and H can fit in.
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~你现在不是在跟基友约会，找辆能坐三个人的车。

E2F1AUD.original: ~z~Speaking of crime, bro, what the fuck are we doing here?
E2F1AUD.translated: ~z~说起犯罪，兄弟，我们又他妈要干啥？
